{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ice Eyes is a Christmas survival horror game taking place at a cabin in the middle of the woods. You're a kid on Christmas break and the winter is hitting hard. You find a children's book called &quot;Ice Eyes&quot; that tells a story of a blood thirsty monster that hunts kids. For the next 3 nights you're the next target of this mysterious beast. The book gives you instructions on how to keep the monster at bay. Build snowmen by rolling snowballs on the ground while avoiding the monster around every corner. Search for answers on how to defeat Ice Eyes for good. Read the clues given in the children's poems to find your next steps. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Snowmen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396950/extras/building-snowman-gif.gif?t=1735413378\" />To keep Ice Eyes at bay, build snowmen. They act as scarecrows that will scare off the monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Throw snowballs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396950/extras/throw-snowballs-gif.gif?t=1735413378\" />Distract the monster by hitting it with snowballs and running away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve the mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396950/extras/mystery-gif.gif?t=1735413378\" />Why do kids keep disappearing in the winter? Why Ice Eyes is hunting you? How do you defeat it?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735413378","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396950/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735413378","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st